bl>); later, epith. of the Moon, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Hymn.Mag.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.3</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n47548.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in later <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a day</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:38:271\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nonn.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">38.271</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2046.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:478\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Q.S.\">Q.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.478</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n47548.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἔαρ</etym>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bearing in spring</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λέαινα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg008:426\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">426</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (nisi leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἠυγ-</foreign>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}